(1, 2, 'Hi Team,\n\nPlease find my End of Day (EOD) report below.\n\n\nBeth Project (Beth)\nLink: https://weavelry.com/\nlogout button (00h 00m)\nGeneral Tasks\nstart working on beth project to add anouncement bar on the top and for seo asked to ashish sir to provide the audit report (00h 03m)\nstart working on beth project to add anouncement bar on the top and for seo asked to ashish sir to provide the audit report https://weavelry.com/dashboard-login/ (00h 43m)\ncreating one plugin for the anouncement bar... (01h 17m)\ncreated one plugin for the beth project where user can create delete anu type of anouncement usig wp-admin area user can change background color, speed, or text color dynamically and also add multiple anouncement bars... (01h 01m)\nnow starts working on the \"John Davis\" client on \"https://thechanginglane.org/\" site and renamming the lane with lanes and also working on the other issues (00h 00m)\nrename the tesxt from lane to lanes \"© 2026 The Changing Lanes. A 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization. EIN: 85-1368325\" (04h 15m)\n\n\nPlease let me know if you have any questions.\n\nThank you,\nKaranbir Singh CMS Developer', '<p>Hello Team,</p>\n\n<p>Please find my End of Day (EOD) report for <strong>June 20, 2024</strong> below.</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2>1. Project Updates</h2>\n\n<h3><strong>Project Name: Beth Project (Weavelry)</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><strong>Page/Task Name:</strong> Announcement Bar Plugin Development, SEO Audit Coordination</li>\n    <li><strong>Design/Preview Link:</strong> <a href=\"https://weavelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://weavelry.com/</a>, <a href=\"https://weavelry.com/dashboard-login/\" target=\"_blank\">https://weavelry.com/dashboard-login/</a></li>\n    <li><strong>Work Completed:</strong>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Initiated development for an announcement bar feature and created a custom plugin.</li>\n            <li>The plugin enables users to create, delete, and manage multiple announcement bars via the WP-admin area.</li>\n            <li>Implemented dynamic customization options for background color, text color, and display speed of announcements.</li>\n            <li>Coordinated with Ashish Sir to request the SEO audit report for the project.</li>\n            <li>Performed a quick check on the \'logout button\' functionality.</li>\n        </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><strong>Work Pending:</strong>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Full integration and comprehensive testing of the announcement bar plugin.</li>\n            <li>Implementation of SEO recommendations upon receipt of the audit report.</li>\n        </ul>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<h3><strong>Project Name: John Davis (The Changing Lane)</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n    <li><strong>Page/Task Name:</strong> Text Renaming and Site Maintenance</li>\n    <li><strong>Design/Preview Link:</strong> <a href=\"https://thechanginglane.org/\" target=\"_blank\">https://thechanginglane.org/</a></li>\n    <li><strong>Work Completed:</strong>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Successfully updated the copyright text from \"lane\" to \"lanes\" on the website (e.g., \"© 2026 The Changing Lanes. A 501(c)(3) nonprofit organization. EIN: 85-1368325\").</li>\n            <li>Addressed several other minor site issues as per client requirements.</li>\n        </ul>\n    </li>\n    <li><strong>Work Pending:</strong>\n        <ul>\n            <li>Further review and resolution of any remaining identified site issues.</li>\n        </ul>\n    </li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2>2. Tracker Status</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li><strong>Total Tracker (Expected for today):</strong> Approximately 8 hours</li>\n    <li><strong>Running Tracker (Reported for today):</strong> Approximately 7 hours 19 minutes</li>\n    <li><strong>Pending Tracker (Remaining for full day):</strong> Approximately 0 hours 41 minutes</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2>3. System Details (Where the tracker was used)</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li><strong>System Seat Number:</strong> Not Provided</li>\n    <li><strong>System Password:</strong> Not Provided</li>\n    <li><strong>Tracker Tabs Open:</strong> Not Provided</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2>4. Client Communication</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>No specific client communications or updates were made today.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<h2>5. Message for BD Team (if applicable)</h2>\n<ul>\n    <li>No specific follow-up requirements for the Night Shift today.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>Please let me know if you have any questions.</p>\n\n<p>Thank you,</p>\n<p>Karanbir Singh<br>CMS Developer</p>\n\n<p><small><em>Note: The reported times and values are approximate and compiled from the daily task log. They may not reflect exact real-time tracking.</em></small></p>', '2026-01-15 12:58:16'),
