Performed initial work/checks on the student dashboard page.</li>\r\n<li>Initiated development on the login OTP functionality page.</li>\r\n<li>Commenced designing for the course page.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Work Pending:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Further development and design iteration on these features.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">2. Tracker Status</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Total Tracker (Expected for today):</strong> Approximately 8 hours</li>\r\n<li><strong>Running Tracker (Actual tracked time):</strong> Approximately 6 hours 52 minutes</li>\r\n<li><strong>Pending Tracker (Remaining for today):</strong> Approximately 1 hour 08 minutes</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">3. System Details (Where the tracker was used)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>System Seat Number:</strong> [Enter Seat No.]</li>\r\n<li><strong>System Password:</strong> [Enter Password]</li>\r\n<li><strong>Tracker Tabs Open:</strong> Please provide an update (Yes/No).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">4. Client Communication</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>No specific updates or messages for the client today.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin-top: 25px; margin-bottom: 5px;\">5. Message for BD Team (if applicable)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>No specific follow-up requirements identified for the night shift at this time.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top: 30px;\">Please let me know if you have any questions.</p>\r\n<p>Thank you,</p>\r\n<p>Karanbir Singh<br>CMS Developer</p>\r\n<p style=\"font-size: 0.8em; color: #777; margin-top: 20px;\"><em>Please note: The time values in this report are approximate and for reporting purposes. These are not actual or exact values.</em></p>                            \r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    \r\n                    <!-- Footer / Signature Section -->\r\n                    <tr>\r