(45, 2, 'info@devprojects.in', 'karanbir@virtualoplossing.com,ajit@virtualoplossing.com,prabnek@virtualoplossing.com,nishant@virtualoplossing.com,sandeep@virtualoplossing.com,', 'February 18, 2026 - EOD Report: Karanbir Singh CMS Developer', '<!DOCTYPE html>\r\n<html lang=\"en\">\r\n<head>\r\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\r\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\r\n    <title>February 18, 2026 - EOD Report: Karanbir Singh CMS Developer</title>\r\n    <style>\r\n        /* Basic responsive styles for email clients that support them */\r\n        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {\r\n            .content-table {\r\n                width: 100% !important;\r\n            }\r\n        }\r\n        div[style*=\"background-color:#FFEB9C\"] {\r\n  display: none !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n    </style>\r\n</head>\r\n<body style=\"margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f7f6;\">\r\n    <table width=\"100%\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" bgcolor=\"#f4f7f6\">\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td align=\"center\" style=\"padding: 20px 0;\">\r\n                \r\n                <!-- Main Email Wrapper Table (600px wide) -->\r\n                <table class=\"content-table\" width=\"600\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" align=\"center\" style=\"background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\">\r\n                    \r\n                    <!-- Header Section -->\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"padding: 30px 40px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;\">\r\n                            <!-- Your company logo -->\r\n                            <img src=\"https://virtualoplossing.com/wp-content/themes/blankslate/assets/img/virtual-oplossing-logo.svg\" alt=\"VirtualOplossing Logo\" width=\"180\" style=\"display: block;\">\r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    \r\n                    <!-- Body Content Section -->\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"padding: 40px 40px 30px 40px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;\">\r\n                            \r\n                            <!-- This is where the dynamic EOD report content will be injected -->\r\n                            <p>Hello Team,</p>\r\n<p>Please find the End of Day (EOD) report&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3>1. Project Updates</h3>\r\n<p><strong>Project Name:</strong> Beth Project (Beth)</p>\r\n<p><strong>Design/Preview Link:</strong> <a href=\"https://weavelry.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">https://weavelry.com/</a></p>\r\n<h4>Work Completed:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>OTP Expiry Bug Resolution:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Client Reported Issue:</strong> \"Logging in &ndash; after login, even when it works, you get a message saying OTP expired. But, you can still log in later.\"</li>\r\n<li><strong>Resolution:</strong> The OTP expiry mechanism has been thoroughly reviewed and corrected. Previously, the system would incorrectly allow login after displaying an \"OTP expired\" message. This behavior is now fixed; login is correctly prevented with an expired OTP, ensuring users are directed to the dashboard only upon entering a valid, non-expired OTP. Extensive testing has confirmed this resolution.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Admin Top Bar Visibility for Standard Users:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Client Reported Issue:</strong> \"Users see a top bar that says \'Weavelry Hostinger Edit home page\' and on the right side it says \'Howdy USERNAME\'. They should not see this bar, but they should see the \'Howdy Username\'. Also, the user was able to log into Hostinger from up there; it needs to go away.\"</li>\r\n<li><strong>Resolution:</strong> The administrative top bar, including the \'Weavelry Hostinger Edit home page\' text and the Hostinger login access, has been successfully removed for standard users. The \'Howdy USERNAME\' greeting remains visible as intended, providing a personalized welcome without exposing administrative functions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Share Projects - Photo Display Enhancements:</strong>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Client Reported Issues:</strong>\r\n<ol type=\"a\">\r\n<li>\"Not showing the whole picture, needs to show entire photo in large photos and small photos below.\"</li>\r\n<li>\"Photo is blurry.\"</li>\r\n<li>\"If someone uploads 2 photos, if another person clicks on that second photo, can it be seen in a large size similar to the first photo?\"</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n<li><strong>Resolution:</strong> All identified issues related to photo display within the \'Share Projects\' functionality have been addressed and resolved.\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Photos now display completely, ensuring the entire image is visible in both large and small formats.</li>\r\n<li>Image clarity has been improved to eliminate blurriness.</li>\r\n<li>The system now correctly allows users to view multiple uploaded photos individually in a large size upon selection, ensuring a consistent viewing experience across all images.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4>Work Pending:</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><em>[Please fill]</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>2. Tracker Status</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>Total Tracker:</strong> <em>6:40 hrs</em></li>\r\n<li><strong>Running Tracker:</strong> <em>6:40 hrs</em></li>\r\n<li><strong>Pending Tracker:</strong> <em>0</em></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>3. System Details (Where the tracker was used)</h3>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><strong>System Seat Number:</strong>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><strong>System Password:</strong>&nbsp;</li>\r\n<li><strong>Tracker Tabs Open:</strong>&nbsp;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3>4. Client Communication</h3>\r\n<p><em>[Any updates/Message for client, in proper format]</em></p>\r\n<h3>5. Message for BD Team (if applicable)</h3>\r\n<p><em>[Follow-up requirements in Night Shift]</em></p>\r\n<p><em><strong>Note:</strong> This report contains approximate values and content generated by an AI assistant and may not reflect exact real-time data.</em></p>                            \r\n                        </td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                    \r\n                    <!-- Footer / Signature Section -->\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td style=\"padding: 0;\">\r\n                            \r\n                            <!-- This is where your custom signature from the database will be injected -->\r\n                            <table style=\"background-color: rgb(15, 45, 62); background-image: url(\'\\\'\\\'\'); background-repeat: repeat; padding: 20px; width: 818px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; height: 130px;\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"padding-right: 20px; width: 246.469px;\" align=\"left\"><!-- Logo and Company Info -->\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><img src=\"https://virtualoplossing.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Virtual-Oplossing-White.svg\" alt=\"Virtual Oplossing Logo\" width=\"180\"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #ffffff; padding-top: 5px;\">We deliver your thoughts</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 232.391px;\" align=\"left\"><!-- Personal Information -->\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #38b6ff;\">Regards,</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 5px 0; font-size: 20px; color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold;\">KARANBIR SINGH</h3>\r\n<p style=\"background-color: #38b6ff; color: #ffffff; font-size: 12px; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block; margin: 0;\">CMS Developer</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style=\"border-left: 2px solid rgb(255, 255, 255); width: 24.5px; padding-left: 20px;\">&nbsp;</td>\r\n<td style=\"width: 268.641px;\" align=\"left\"><!-- Contact Information -->\r\n<table border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=