(24, 2, 'Working on changes', '2026-01-29', 'I broke something when I was playing around. It no longer sends email to people when they join. (Or was this broken when they cancelled the email and wanted us to pay?) I now have an alias that works. The alias is through hostinger: info@weavelry.com. It forwards mail to my gmail account, bmckinney 60@gmail.com. Can you make sure this alias will work and is connected to all the mail links??? Including all the ways to contact us.\r\nSolution :- fixed change smto to info@weavelry email now user receive all images from info\r\nCan you limit people to two photos per shared project?\r\nSolution:- added validation that user only able to post 2 images and able to delete uploaded images\r\nCan you allow people to edit photos in shared project (you allow them to add, but not delete).\r\nSolution:-added delete buttons user able to delete\r\n \r\n\r\nThat is it for now. I am getting familiar with the back end. So I can manage some stuff myself. If this is a success, there will be much more coming your way. Beta testing is going well.\r\n\r\nCheck Gmail Messages and work as per requirement.', '2026-01-29 09:53:57', '2026-01-29 15:24:18', 1, '2026-01-29 07:23:57'),
