(33, 2, 'Issue in site', '2026-02-04', 'Client message:\r\n\r\nHi Moninder - I sent Prabnek a text from a user who had problems. I\'m not sure if you heard about that earlier today. I also had some friends try to log in on their phones tonight. When you click log in from a phone, it takes you to \"projects.\" That was confusing. Also, they did the osp login and still could not log in. Can you assist? I need this to work before reaching out to future members. Thanks so much, Beth.\r\n\r\n\r\nDeveloper messege:- issue fixed this is only come due to multiple antivirus plugins installed in the site so when i remove this, site starts workling fine now', '2026-02-04 10:00:58', '2026-02-04 10:43:43', 1, '2026-02-04 04:30:58'),
