(37, 2, 'create all modules test report', '2026-02-05', 'creating one excel file to create a test report of all module which i worked on it\r\n\r\n\r\nWeavelry Site Testing Summary\r\n🔐 Authentication\r\n\r\nLogin via password – Working\r\n\r\nLogin via OTP – Working\r\n\r\n🧶 Pattern Management (Frontend)\r\n\r\nAdd pattern – Working\r\n\r\nEdit pattern – Working\r\n\r\nDelete pattern – Working\r\n\r\n📌 Project (Share Project)\r\n\r\nAdd new project – Working\r\n\r\nEdit project / Like / Bookmark – Working\r\n\r\nDelete project – Working\r\n\r\nIssue: Redirected to wrong URL after delete\r\n\r\nStatus: Fixed\r\n\r\n❓ Question & Answer Module\r\n\r\nAdd new question – Working\r\n\r\nQuestion detail view – Working\r\n\r\nIssue: Breadcrumb redirected to wrong URL\r\n\r\nStatus: Fixed\r\n\r\nShare button on Q&A – Working\r\n\r\nUnanswered questions auto-added to Unanswered tab – Working\r\n\r\nEdit/Delete Q&A from frontend – Restricted\r\n\r\nReason: Community posts are admin-controlled and can only be deleted from admin panel\r\n\r\n🎥 Video Module\r\n\r\nAdd new video – Working\r\n\r\nEdit video – Working\r\n\r\nDelete video – Working\r\n\r\n🛒 Buy & Sell (Marketplace)\r\n\r\nAdd new product – Working\r\n\r\nEdit product – Working\r\n\r\nDelete product – Working\r\n\r\n⚙️ Backend (Admin Panel) Testing\r\n📊 Admin Utilities\r\n\r\nStats dashboard – Working\r\n\r\nOne-click copy all emails – Working\r\n\r\nProblem reports management – Working\r\n\r\n📁 Content Management\r\n\r\nManage projects – Working\r\n\r\nAdd projects – Working\r\n\r\nView patterns – Working\r\n\r\nAdd new patterns – Working\r\n\r\nPattern keywords/tags – Working\r\n\r\nManage Q&A (add/edit/delete) – Working\r\n\r\nManage videos (add/edit/delete) – Working\r\n\r\nManage video tags – Working\r\n\r\n🏪 Marketplace (Backend)\r\n\r\nManage marketplace listings – Working\r\n\r\nAdd new products from backend – Working\r\n\r\nRecommendation: Prefer frontend for product creation\r\n\r\nManage marketplace notifications – Working\r\n\r\n💬 Comments & Notifications\r\n\r\nManage comments – Working\r\n\r\nNotification control (users/admins) – Working\r\n\r\nBuy & Sell notification control – Working', '2026-02-05 10:09:25', '2026-02-05 12:24:53', 1, '2026-02-05 04:39:25'),
