(62, 2, 'SSH setup', '2026-02-24', 'setup ssh on web and documet is given below which i prepare \r\n\r\n📘 COMPLETE DEPLOYMENT GUIDE\r\nSecure Web SSH via Cloudflare Tunnel + ttyd\r\n\r\n🎯 Architecture Overview\r\nBrowser\r\n  ↓\r\nCloudflare (HTTPS + SSL)\r\n  ↓\r\nCloudflare Tunnel\r\n  ↓\r\nlocalhost:7681\r\n  ↓\r\nttyd\r\n  ↓\r\n/bin/bash (SSH shell)\r\n✔ No open ports\r\n ✔ No public IP required\r\n ✔ Works behind NAT\r\n ✔ Secure encrypted access\r\n\r\n1️⃣ Install Required Packages\r\nsudo apt update\r\nsudo apt install ttyd cloudflared -y\r\nVerify:\r\nttyd --version\r\ncloudflared --version\r\n\r\n2️⃣ Authenticate Cloudflare\r\ncloudflared tunnel login\r\nBrowser will open\r\n\r\n\r\nSelect your domain\r\n\r\n\r\nAuthorize\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n3️⃣ Create Tunnel\r\ncloudflared tunnel create ubuntu-ssh\r\nThis creates:\r\n~/.cloudflared/\r\n ├── TUNNEL_ID.json\r\n\r\n4️⃣ Create Tunnel Configuration\r\nCreate config:\r\nnano ~/.cloudflared/config.yml\r\nPaste:\r\ntunnel: ubuntu-ssh\r\ncredentials-file: /home/YOUR_USER/.cloudflared/TUNNEL_ID.json\r\n\r\ningress:\r\n - hostname: ssh.yourdomain.com\r\n   service: http://localhost:7681\r\n - service: http_status:404\r\nReplace:\r\nYOUR_USER\r\n\r\n\r\nTUNNEL_ID.json\r\n\r\n\r\nssh.yourdomain.com\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n5️⃣ Create DNS Route\r\ncloudflared tunnel route dns ubuntu-ssh ssh.yourdomain.com\r\n\r\n6️⃣ Start ttyd (Correct Command)\r\n⚠ IMPORTANT FOR ttyd 1.7.4:\r\n-W = writable mode\r\n\r\n\r\n-w = working directory\r\n\r\n\r\nCorrect command:\r\nttyd -i 127.0.0.1 -p 7681 -W -- /bin/bash -il\r\nExpected output:\r\nListening on port: 7681\r\n\r\n7️⃣ Start Tunnel\r\ncloudflared tunnel run ubuntu-ssh\r\nExpected:\r\nRegistered tunnel connection\r\nNow open:\r\nhttps://ssh.yourdomain.com\r\nYou should see:\r\nuser@hostname:~$\r\n\r\n8️⃣ Make It Auto-Start on Boot\r\n\r\n🔹 A. Configure ttyd Service\r\nCreate service:\r\nsudo nano /etc/systemd/system/ttyd.service\r\nPaste:\r\n[Unit]\r\nDescription=ttyd Web Terminal\r\nAfter=network.target\r\n\r\n[Service]\r\nType=simple\r\nUser=YOUR_USER\r\nWorkingDirectory=/home/YOUR_USER\r\nExecStart=/usr/bin/ttyd -i 127.0.0.1 -p 7681 -W -- /bin/bash -il\r\nRestart=always\r\nRestartSec=5\r\n\r\n[Install]\r\nWantedBy=multi-user.target\r\nEnable:\r\nsudo systemctl daemon-reload\r\nsudo systemctl enable ttyd\r\nsudo systemctl start ttyd\r\nCheck:\r\nsudo systemctl status ttyd\r\n\r\n🔹 B. Configure Cloudflared Service\r\nMove config to system path:\r\nsudo mkdir -p /etc/cloudflared\r\nsudo cp ~/.cloudflared/* /etc/cloudflared/\r\nEdit:\r\nsudo nano /etc/cloudflared/config.yml\r\nChange credentials path to:\r\ncredentials-file: /etc/cloudflared/TUNNEL_ID.json\r\nInstall service:\r\nsudo cloudflared service install\r\nsudo systemctl enable cloudflared\r\nsudo systemctl start cloudflared\r\nVerify:\r\nsudo systemctl status cloudflared\r\n\r\n9️⃣ Test After Reboot\r\nsudo reboot\r\nAfter reboot:\r\nhttps://ssh.yourdomain.com\r\nShould work automatically.\r\n\r\n🚨 Common Errors & Fixes\r\n\r\n❌ Error: connect: connection refused\r\nCause:\r\nttyd not running\r\n\r\n\r\nFix:\r\nsudo systemctl start ttyd\r\n\r\n❌ Error: Black Screen + Reconnecting\r\nCause:\r\nUsed -w instead of -W\r\n\r\n\r\nFix:\r\nttyd -W -- /bin/bash -il\r\n\r\n❌ Error: ttyd: missing start command\r\nCause:\r\nForgot --\r\n\r\n\r\nFix:\r\nttyd -W -- /bin/bash\r\n\r\n❌ Error: Cannot determine config path\r\nCause:\r\nConfig not in /etc/cloudflared\r\n\r\n\r\nFix:\r\nsudo cp ~/.cloudflared/* /etc/cloudflared/\r\n\r\n🔐 Recommended Security Hardening\r\n\r\n1️⃣ Bind Only to Localhost\r\n-i 127.0.0.1\r\nPrevents LAN access.\r\n\r\n2️⃣ Enable Cloudflare Zero Trust\r\nInside Cloudflare dashboard:\r\nZero Trust → Access → Applications → Add Application\r\nProtect:\r\nssh.yourdomain.com\r\nEnable:\r\nGoogle login\r\n\r\n\r\nEmail OTP\r\n\r\n\r\nMFA\r\n\r\n\r\nThen remove ttyd password flag.\r\n\r\n3️⃣ Enable Firewall\r\nsudo ufw enable\r\nsudo ufw deny 7681\r\n\r\n🏆 Final Production Setup Summary\r\n✔ No open ports\r\n ✔ No static IP required\r\n ✔ Encrypted HTTPS\r\n ✔ Auto start on reboot\r\n ✔ Behind Cloudflare security\r\n ✔ Bound to localhost\r\n ✔ Optional MFA\r\n\r\n📌 To Deploy On Another System\r\nJust repeat:\r\nInstall packages\r\n\r\n\r\nLogin cloudflared\r\n\r\n\r\nCreate tunnel\r\n\r\n\r\nCreate config\r\n\r\n\r\nCreate services\r\n\r\n\r\nEnable services\r\n\r\n\r\nDone.', '2026-02-24 18:28:56', '2026-02-24 18:28:58', 42, '2026-02-24 12:58:56'),
