(84, 2, 'Resolve new issues', '2026-03-06', 'Hi @Sandeep Bhardwaj\r\nI wanted to give you an update on the ongoing plugin review for “bulk-page-creator”.\r\nCurrent Status:\r\nThe plugin has been manually reviewed by WordPress volunteers.\r\nSeveral issues have been identified that prevent approval.\r\nKey Issues to Address:\r\nInvalid URLs – Some plugin URLs are timing out or unreachable.\r\nUndocumented Source Code – JavaScript/CSS source files need to be made public or documented to comply with WordPress guidelines.\r\nImproper Script and Style Loading – JS and CSS are not using wp_enqueue_* functions; currently some code is included inline.\r\nUndocumented Third-Party Services – Plugin calls external APIs (e.g., vopharma.in) but this is not documented in the readme.\r\nDirect Core File Calls – Some WordPress core files are being included directly, which is discouraged for security and compatibility reasons.\r\nGlobal PHP Sessions – session_start() is being triggered on all pages, which may conflict with caching and affect performance.\r\nNext Steps / Action Plan:\r\nReview each issue carefully and implement fixes according to WordPress guidelines.\r\nTest updated plugin on a clean WordPress installation with WP_DEBUG enabled.\r\nUpdate the readme to document third-party services and source code availability.\r\nResubmit the corrected version for review.\r\nI will continue working on these updates and ensure the plugin is fully compliant before resubmission.', '2026-03-06 10:47:13', '2026-03-06 11:06:38', 52, '2026-03-06 05:17:13'),
(85, 2, '500 issue face by kajal lets resolve this', '2026-03-06', '500 issue face by kajal lets resolve this\r\nInformed to kajal on her seat and she played the settings and now issue is resolved', '2026-03-06 11:06:38', NULL, 39, '2026-03-06 05:36:38');
