(46, 2, 'Amir Rasouli | Contract ID 42509788', 'Active', 'Amir Rasouli', 'https://o-so-cute-2.myshopify.com/admin', 'Fixed', 'Hi Moninder.\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nThe appearance will be exactly the same.\r\nIt will require registration for the customer and a mechanism that would\r\nallow us to approve the account, because we would have to ask for them to\r\nprovide a sales permit for tax exemption. Not sure of the customer flow...\r\nI\'m still considering free shipping thresholds for both retail and\r\nwholesale.\r\nI\'ve also made table items, dimensions, weights and various box sizes that\r\nare triggered by quantity. Can you help set that up in Shippo later?\r\nPricing as follows:\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nWholesale Prices:\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n10” Frame - $49 Clearance sale!\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n7” Acrylic - $49\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\n7” Book - $39\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nOrb - $39\r\n\r\n \r\n\r\nHeartbeat recorder - $6', NULL, '2026-02-04 08:29:53'),
