(48, 2, 'simple Marketing GmbH & Co KG', 'Active', 'Manuel R. (.simple Marketing GmbH & Co KG) (Contract ID: 42092892)- Moninder Kaur', 'https://Stagingdev34.rechteasy.at ', 'Fixed', 'Hello Team\r\n\r\nWe’ve received a WordPress-related task from the Manuel ( client ) regarding fixing Google Search Console errors.\r\n\r\nThe client has provided Google Console\'s access using our email virtualoplossing0@gmail.com.\r\n\r\nClient has also set up a staging server for us and shared the required credentials.\r\n\r\nURL: Stagingdev34.rechteasy.at \r\nUsername: Virtualoplossing \r\nPassword: mqW7PqHg82u5jCLYGj8YqCS(\r\n\r\nAdditionally, the client has shared the plugin files and the theme’s functions.php file. I’m attaching the same here for your review.\r\n\r\nPlease check and let me know if anything else is required from my side or if we need to request any additional information or access from the client.\r\n\r\nThanks,', NULL, '2026-02-09 06:50:21'),
