(788, 2, 'Final Polish & Cache Purge: Implement any minor client feedback and perform a final \"Purge Everything\".', '2025-10-07 18:31:24', '2025-10-07 18:33:27', '2025-10-07', '2025-10-07 13:01:24', NULL, NULL),
(800, 2, 'Ozgur project Today is focused on establishing a solid foundation. I will begin by verifying access to all necessary accounts (Cloudflare, Webflow, GoDaddy) and retrieving the dedicated IP for the WordPress installation. The main task will be reconfiguring the Cloudflare DNS: I will delete any old records, add the two required Webflow proxy A records for the root domain, and create the service-page A record pointing to the GoDaddy IP, ensuring its proxy status is set to \"Proxied\". To conclude the day, I will set the Cloudflare SSL/TLS mode to \"Full (Strict)\" to ensure secure end-to-end connections.', '2025-09-27 21:58:48', '2025-09-27 22:37:53', '2025-09-27', '2025-10-07 13:07:48', NULL, NULL),
(801, 2, 'This day is dedicated to deploying the Cloudflare Worker, which acts as the reverse proxy\'s logic. I will start by creating the omnilink-router Worker, deleting the default template, and deploying the final script that routes traffic to either poplin2.webflow.io or the WordPress origin. Immediately after, I will activate it by configuring a single \"Custom Domain\" route in the Worker\'s settings, set to *omnilinkciruits.com/*. To end the day, I will use the Worker\'s real-time logs to verify that requests to the root domain and the /service-page subdirectory are correctly identified and routed.', '2025-09-29 22:15:53', '2025-09-29 23:37:57', '2025-09-29', '2025-10-07 13:07:53', NULL, NULL),
(806, 2, 'Today\'s objective is to fully integrate the WordPress installation on GoDaddy, making it completely \"aware\" that it operates behind a proxy. This is a critical step to prevent WordPress from breaking the seamless user experience by generating incorrect URLs or causing redirect loops, which is a common issue in such setups. The goal is to make the WordPress backend and frontend fully compatible with the proxied environment.', '2025-10-01 12:39:44', '2025-10-01 15:51:47', '2025-10-01', '2025-10-07 13:21:44', NULL, NULL),
(807, 2, 'The technical work will be performed on the GoDaddy server using the File Manager. First, I will edit the wp-config.php file, adding WP_HOME and WP_SITEURL definitions to hardcode the public-facing URL structure. Second, I will edit the .htaccess file, replacing its contents with a corrected ruleset that includes the RewriteBase /service-page/ directive. This combination forces WordPress to generate all links correctly and tells the server how to handle routing within the subdirectory.', '2025-10-01 15:52:47', '2025-10-01 16:25:50', '2025-10-01', '2025-10-07 13:21:47', NULL, NULL),
(808, 2, 'Upon completion, the WordPress integration will be stable and fully functional. I will verify this by logging into the WordPress admin area via the main proxied URL (https://omnilinkciruits.com/wp-admin/) and navigating through the backend. A successful outcome means all pages load correctly without any redirects to the internal service-page subdomain, confirming that WordPress is now fully compatible with the reverse proxy.', '2025-10-01 18:52:50', '2025-10-01 21:45:50', '2025-10-01', '2025-10-07 13:21:50', NULL, NULL),
(809, 2, 'Upon completion, the WordPress integration will be stable and fully functional. I will verify this by logging into the WordPress admin area via the main proxied URL (https://omnilinkciruits.com/wp-admin/) and navigating through the backend. A successful outcome means all pages load correctly without any redirects to the internal service-page subdomain, confirming that WordPress is now fully compatible with the reverse proxy.', '2025-10-01 16:25:50', '2025-10-01 18:51:53', '2025-10-01', '2025-10-07 13:21:50', NULL, NULL),
(810, 2, 'The focus of  to ensure the entire hybrid setup is technically sound for SEO. The primary goal is to consolidate all domain authority under the single omnilinkciruits.com domain and eliminate any risk of being penalized by search engines for duplicate content, which is a common and serious pitfall of reverse proxy configurations.', '2025-10-01 21:45:53', '2025-10-02 00:40:56', '2025-10-01', '2025-10-07 13:21:53', NULL, NULL),
(811, 2, 'The first action will be to log into the Webflow project settings and configure the \"Custom canonical tag URL\" to https://omnilinkciruits.com, after which I will re-publish the entire site. This forces Webflow to output the correct canonical tag on all its pages. The second action will be to log into the WordPress admin dashboard on GoDaddy and enable the \"Discourage search engines from indexing this site\" option. This critical step adds a noindex tag to the origin subdomain, hiding it from Google.', '2025-10-02 13:51:56', '2025-10-02 17:51:59', '2025-10-02', '2025-10-07 13:21:56', NULL, NULL),
(812, 2, 'By the end of the day, the technical SEO foundation will be solid. When inspecting the source code of any page—whether from Webflow or WordPress—the canonical tag will correctly point to the main domain. The WordPress origin will be completely hidden from search engine crawlers, preventing any duplicate content issues and ensuring all SEO value is attributed to omnilinkciruits.com.', '2025-10-02 17:52:59', '2025-10-02 19:47:05', '2025-10-02', '2025-10-07 13:21:59', NULL, NULL),
(813, 2, 'Today is dedicated entirely to rigorous quality assurance. The objective is to perform a comprehensive, end-to-end test of the entire integrated website from the perspective of a user, identifying any functional bugs, visual glitches, or broken user journeys before the final review. The goal is to ensure the hybrid site feels like a single, cohesive platform.', '2025-10-02 19:48:05', '2025-10-02 23:35:08', '2025-10-02', '2025-10-07 13:22:05', NULL, NULL),
(814, 2, 'The testing process will be systematic. I will click through all navigation links, ensuring the transition between Webflow and WordPress pages is seamless. I will test all interactive elements, such as contact forms on both platforms, and verify all internal links to confirm they use the correct omnilinkciruits.com URL structure. This will be followed by cross-browser and mobile device testing to check for any responsive design issues or platform-specific bugs.', '2025-10-03 10:52:08', '2025-10-03 12:52:11', '2025-10-03', '2025-10-07 13:22:08', NULL, NULL),
(815, 2, 'The deliverable for today will be a clear and concise bug report. All findings from the QA process will be logged with detailed steps to reproduce. This document will create a formal action plan for the final bug-fixing phase, ensuring that all known issues are tracked and resolved before the project is considered complete.', '2025-10-03 12:52:11', '2025-10-03 15:24:14', '2025-10-03', '2025-10-07 13:22:11', NULL, NULL),
(816, 2, 'This process is critical for transitioning the application from a development state to a stable, production-ready build.', '2025-10-03 12:52:14', '2025-10-03 14:00:21', '2025-10-03', '2025-10-07 13:22:14', NULL, NULL),
(817, 2, 'This validation also includes smoke testing core functionalities to ensure the patches have not introduced any regressions or side-effects into the system\'s baseline behavior.', '2025-10-03 14:01:21', '2025-10-03 15:52:27', '2025-10-03', '2025-10-07 13:22:21', NULL, NULL),
(818, 2, 'The first action will be to perform a final \"Purge Everything\" in the Cloudflare cache, which pushes all recent fixes live globally. Following this, I will create a comprehensive technical document. This document will contain the final, working versions of the Cloudflare Worker script, the WordPress .htaccess rules, and the wp-config.php additions, serving as a permanent record of the configuration.', '2025-10-06 23:15:27', '2025-10-07 19:27:01', '2025-10-06', '2025-10-07 13:22:27', NULL, NULL),
(819, 2, 'After deploying fixes, I will perform regression testing to confirm the solutions work as expected.', '2025-10-03 15:59:09', '2025-10-03 16:49:16', '2025-10-03', '2025-10-07 13:52:09', NULL, NULL),
(820, 2, 'Monitor the first few real affiliate orders closely to ensure everything is working as expected.', '2025-10-03 23:50:20', '2025-10-04 00:35:00', '2025-10-03', '2025-10-07 13:53:20', NULL, NULL),
