(876, 2, 'Centralized Content Hub (The Google Sheet): You now have a structured spreadsheet that acts as the single source of truth for dozens or hundreds of pages. Instead of logging into WordPress for every edit, your team can manage everything—from page titles and hero content to dynamic FAQs and custom sections—in a familiar, collaborative environment.', '2025-10-30 17:51:43', '2025-10-30 17:51:50', '2025-10-30', '2025-10-30 12:21:43', NULL, NULL),
(877, 2, 'Intelligent Automation (The Google Apps Script): We created a sophisticated script with three key automated functions: AI-Powered Content Parsing: A \"Fill Row From Text\" feature uses the Gemini API to read an entire unstructured document and intelligently populate all the columns in your sheet, saving hours of manual data entry. Automatic Image Management: A \"Sideload Images\" function automatically scans your sheet for external image URLs, downloads them to your WordPress server, and updates the sheet with the new, local URLs. Smart Syncing: A single \"Run Full Sync\" button orchestrates the entire workflow, first processing images and then creating or updating the corresponding pages in WordPress based on their status.', '2025-10-30 17:51:50', '2025-10-30 17:51:50', '2025-10-30', '2025-10-30 12:21:50', NULL, NULL),
(878, 2, 'Intelligent Automation (The Google Apps Script): We created a sophisticated script with three key automated functions: AI-Powered Content Parsing: A \"Fill Row From Text\" feature uses the Gemini API to read an entire unstructured document and intelligently populate all the columns in your sheet, saving hours of manual data entry. Automatic Image Management: A \"Sideload Images\" function automatically scans your sheet for external image URLs, downloads them to your WordPress server, and updates the sheet with the new, local URLs. Smart Syncing: A single \"Run Full Sync\" button orchestrates the entire workflow, first processing images and then creating or updating the corresponding pages in WordPress based on their status.', '2025-10-30 17:51:50', '2025-10-30 17:51:56', '2025-10-30', '2025-10-30 12:21:50', NULL, NULL),
(879, 2, 'Secure & Flexible Backend (The WordPress Plugin): Instead of risky theme modifications, all the server-side logic now resides in a self-contained plugin. This includes: Custom API Endpoints: Secure routes for creating pages, updating pages, and processing images, all protected by a secret API key. Dynamic Page Templating: The plugin uses master HTML and CSS templates to ensure every generated page is pixel-perfect, responsive, and consistent with your brand design. Admin Control Panel: A user-friendly settings page in the WordPress admin area allows you to configure your API key, default images, and other settings without ever touching code.', '2025-10-30 17:51:56', '2025-10-30 17:52:02', '2025-10-30', '2025-10-30 12:21:56', NULL, NULL),
(880, 2, 'User-Friendly Tools (The Private Media Uploader): To support the content creation process, we built a password-protected, front-end Media Uploader tool. This utility page allows non-admin users to either upload files directly or paste external URLs to have images automatically imported into the WordPress Media Library, making it incredibly easy to get the URLs needed for the Google Sheet.', '2025-10-30 17:52:02', '2025-10-30 17:52:10', '2025-10-30', '2025-10-30 12:22:02', NULL, NULL),
(881, 2, 'Massive Time & Cost Savings: The biggest benefit is efficiency. The time it takes to create 100 pages is now virtually the same as creating one. This drastically reduces the labor costs associated with content entry and site management. Scalability on Demand: Your ability to launch new campaigns, target new locations, or add new product lines is no longer limited by manual effort. You can scale your website\'s content as fast as you can fill out a spreadsheet. Unbreakable Brand Consistency: By using a single set of templates, every page is guaranteed to have a consistent layout, style, and functionality. This eliminates the \"human error\" factor and ensures a professional user experience. Empowerment of Non-Technical Teams: Your content writers, SEO specialists, and marketing team can now be in full control of their content pipeline. They can create and update pages using a tool they already know (Google Sheets), without needing WordPress training or admin access. Improved Site Performance & Reliability: The automatic image sideloading feature is crucial. By hosting all images on your own server, your pages will load faster and you\'ll never have to worry about broken images if an external source goes down. This is better for both user experience and SEO. Professional & Distributable Asset: By packaging everything into a well-structured plugin with a settings page and instructions, you have created a professional, maintainable, and potentially sellable piece of software that is not dependent on a specific theme.', '2025-10-30 17:52:10', '2025-10-30 17:52:14', '2025-10-30', '2025-10-30 12:22:10', NULL, NULL),
