(1018, 2, 'Client Message :  For the Buy/Sell 1. For people who want to sell, can it be simple, like title and description? If it gets too big, we can add categories, but for now, I imaging people will want to scroll and see everything for sale. Is there a way for the seller to be contacted? Like button that says contact seller that somehow allows you to email them? Otherwise, the seller will have to show a way to contact them. 2. For buyers , a button that says \"I\'m looking for.....\" and allow them to post a loom they are looking for and a way to be contacted as well.     start working on this part', '2025-12-18 10:12:52', '2025-12-18 17:55:21', '2025-12-18', '2025-12-18 04:42:52', NULL, NULL),
