(1124, 2, 'Social links and email system', '2026-01-19 11:00:38', '2026-01-19 14:05:36', '2026-01-19', '2026-01-19 06:00:38', 'Start working on beth project email system , add social links in footer,  \r\nLooks good to me. Also:\r\n1. I have a weavelry.com facebook page. Yes - I changed my mind. Here\'s the link. https://www.facebook.com/ (dev notes \"please provide me the correct facebook page url  this is not redirecting you your facebook page...\"?)\r\nSo you can add back the facebook icon wherever appropriate.\r\n2. Do I have a weavelry email? If so, I\'d like to use that to reach out to potential members.\r\n3. So I understand what I have: Hostinger is where we design the webpage. Wordpress is where people can see the webpage. The domain name is still under Squarespace until we can officially transfer it to Wordpress. I would like to learn how to manage my own website eventually.\r\n4. Is there a list of users and their emails? In case I want to email them?\r\n5. Is there a hit counter I can check?', 1),
(1125, 2, 'Changes on site till 19-jan-2026', '2026-01-19 14:05:36', '2026-01-19 15:06:08', '2026-01-19', '2026-01-19 09:35:36', 'Home Page – change “Learn More” button text to Patterns, Your Projects, Weaving Advice, Buy/Sell – to match title.    completed', 1),
