(1127, 2, 'Changes on site till 19-jan-2026', '2026-01-19 18:10:01', '2026-01-19 18:10:23', '2026-01-19', '2026-01-19 12:40:01', '6.	Contact Page: Do I have an email info@weavelry.com? If not, I can get one from wordpress or squarespace, right? As part of owning the domain? Also, delete phone number. Also, add back facebook page. https://www.facebook.com/profile.php?id=61586274644605', 1),
(1128, 2, 'Changes on site till 19-jan-2026', '2026-01-19 18:10:23', '2026-01-19 18:11:40', '2026-01-19', '2026-01-19 12:40:23', '8.	Don’t need radio button and each option. Either hide the options if they aren’t chosen, or put a submit button at the end of each option  fixed', 1),
(1129, 2, 'Changes on site till 19-jan-2026', '2026-01-19 18:11:40', '2026-01-19 18:14:20', '2026-01-19', '2026-01-19 12:41:40', '12.	Important from Beth: Users should be able to edit or delete the patterns they upload.   butto added', 1),
