(1148, 2, 'working on frontend proce show the whole sale price', '2026-02-05 12:30:29', '2026-02-05 18:00:22', '2026-02-05', '2026-02-05 07:00:29', 'working on frontend proce show the whole sale price\r\nalso attend the meeting with ines who support this wholesale functionality and she guide me how can i  change price on frontend lets start working on it\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nCore Pricing Logic Integration: Successfully updated the central snippets/price.liquid file to include BSS B2B data attributes, ensuring that wholesale pricing logic is available globally across the theme.\r\nProduct Grid Optimization: Modified snippets/product-card.liquid to display wholesale prices on collection pages while ensuring that product images, titles, and layouts remain fully visible and intact.\r\nInfinite Scroll Compatibility: Updated the main-collection-product-grid.liquid JavaScript logic to include a BSS refresh callback. This ensures that when new products load via infinite scroll (Ajaxinate), the wholesale prices are automatically applied to the new items.\r\nProduct Detail Page (PDP) Update: Integrated B2B attributes into sections/main-product.liquid, allowing logged-in wholesalers to see their custom pricing directly on the main product page.\r\nDynamic Variant Price Switching: Enhanced the theme.js file with custom event listeners that trigger a price refresh whenever a customer changes product options (like size or color), ensuring the correct wholesale variant price is displayed instantly.\r\nFull Cart Page Integration: Updated sections/cart-template.liquid to reflect wholesale rates for individual line items, original prices, and the final subtotal.\r\nMini-Cart Drawer Support: Modified the dynamic side-cart drawer in both snippets/mini-cart.liquid and the theme’s AJAX JavaScript (theme.js) to show wholesale prices and totals in the side-view basket.\r\nSticky Cart Functionality: Applied B2B data attributes to the sticky-cart.liquid snippet so that the floating \"Add to Cart\" bar correctly displays discounted wholesale rates.\r\nPredictive Search Results: Updated snippets/predictive-search.liquid to ensure that wholesale prices are visible within the search dropdown results as customers type.\r\nCross-sell & Upsell Logic: Configured B2B triggers for the Upsell modal and Cross-sell recommendation blocks, ensuring that all promotional areas on the site respect the \"wholesale\" customer tag.', 46),
(1149, 2, 'setup shippo', '2026-02-12 10:20:09', '2026-02-12 16:53:48', '2026-02-12', '2026-02-12 05:50:09', 'Credencials received from client about shippo lets setup shippo in the site\r\n\r\ndeveloper notes :- price of the shipping material is added successfully and also install and connect the shippo with the store now i asked some given below question to the client and am waiting for the result response\r\n\r\n\r\nMoninder Kaur\r\n4:51 PM\r\nI have one more question. Currently, I set the packing material box price at 0.68 for quantities between 8 and 12. If the quantity exceeds 12, it shows free shipping. What should I do in this case? Do you want to offer free shipping for quantities above 12, or should I continue adding the 0.68 charge for quantities from 12 to infinity?\r\nHi Amir Rasouli could you please elaborate in detail on what type of services you expect from Shippo? What specific features are you looking for, and what functionalities would you like to integrate into your site?', 46),
(1150, 2, 'search on shopify with shippo', '2026-02-17 17:35:36', '2026-02-17 18:35:45', '2026-02-17', '2026-02-17 13:05:36', 'research about this and send complete research email to client by sandy sir and waiting for response and also one hour tracker run by today    \r\n\r\nThank you for clarifying your expectations regarding Shippo and real-time shipping quotes. I completely understand that you would like customers to see accurate, real-time carrier shipping rates at checkout based on their address, while using your current address (470 Stonewood St, Downey CA 90241) for testing.\r\nI’ve reviewed the setup requirements, and I’d like to explain the available options:\r\n1️⃣ Real-Time Carrier Shipping Rates (Preferred Option)\r\nTo display real-time shipping quotes from carriers (UPS, USPS, FedEx, etc.) directly at Shopify checkout via Shippo, Shopify requires “Carrier Calculated Shipping” (CCS) to be enabled. This is available on:\r\nShopify Advanced plan, or\r\nAs an add-on (typically around $20/month) on certain plans if Shopify Support enables it.\r\nIf CCS is enabled, Shippo can pull live carrier rates and automatically display them at checkout as intended.\r\n2️⃣ Alternative Without Plan Change (No Real-Time Rates)\r\nIf you prefer not to upgrade or add CCS, we can still integrate Shippo for label generation and tracking, but checkout shipping rates would need to be:\r\nFlat rate (e.g., standard shipping fee), or\r\nWeight-based rates (more flexible and closer to real pricing).\r\nIn this case, Shippo would still generate labels and tracking after the order is placed, but customers would not see live carrier rates during checkout.\r\n3️⃣ Recommended Path\r\nIf real-time carrier quotes at checkout are a priority, I recommend contacting Shopify support to ask about enabling Carrier Calculated Shipping as an add-on. This is usually more cost-effective than upgrading the entire plan.\r\nPlease let me know how you’d like to proceed:\r\nEnable real-time shipping (via CCS), or\r\nUse weight-based / flat-rate shipping and keep the current plan.\r\nOnce confirmed, I will configure everything accordingly and proceed with testing using the temporary address provided.\r\nLooking forward to your guidance.', 46),
(1151, 2, 'working on otp expiry bug', '2026-02-18 10:09:31', '2026-02-18 13:16:26', '2026-02-18', '2026-02-18 04:39:31', 'client msg - Logging in – after login, even when it works, you get a message saying OTP expired. But, you can still log in later.\r\nDeveloper note- otp send to the email address and now wait for 10 second to expire otp   \r\nsolution :- checked 4 times send otp first and then wait for 10 mins to expire  and then  add exxpired otp in form and press login, it only shows error that otp expired   it never go inside the dashboard...', 1),
(1152, 2, 'working on otp expiry bug', '2026-02-18 15:01:30', '2026-02-18 18:25:54', '2026-02-18', '2026-02-18 09:31:30', 'client msg - Logging in – after login, even when it works, you get a message saying OTP expired. But, you can still log in later.\r\nDeveloper note- otp send to the email address and now wait for 10 second to expire otp   \r\nsolution :- checked 4 times send otp first and then wait for 10 mins to expire  and then  add exxpired otp in form and press login, it only shows error that otp expired   it never go inside the dashboard...\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Logging in – after login, even when it works, you get a message saying OTP expired. But, you can still log in later.\r\n\r\n2. Users see a top bar that says Weavelry Hostinger Edit home page and on the right side it says Howdy USERNAME. They should not see this bar, but they should see the Howdy Username. Also, the user was able to log into hostinger from up there; it needs to go away.\r\n\r\n3. For Share Projects:\r\n\r\na. Not showing the whole picture, needs to show entire photo in large photos and small photos below.\r\n\r\nb. Photo is blurry.\r\n\r\nc. If someone uploads 2 photos, if another person clicks on that second photo, can it be seen in a large size similar to the first photo?\r\n\r\ndeveloper  notes   resolved all errors', 1),
(1153, 2, 'Wordpress website Changes', '2026-02-19 10:31:29', '2026-02-19 16:40:13', '2026-02-19', '2026-02-19 05:51:29', '1. When selecting the \"promotional products\" tab, I would like \"https://www.promoplace.com/anchor-printing-services/\" to display in an iframe width of the page and no scroll bars.\r\n\r\nhttps://www.anchormsp.com/promotional-products/ The page is now displaying in full width correctly. However, the right-side scrollbar cannot be hidden because doing so causes functionality and layout issues. Since the content is being loaded inside an iframe from an external source, browser security restrictions prevent us from fully controlling or modifying the iframe’s internal scrolling behavior.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAdditionally, regarding https://exhibitbook.com/\r\n— if this website belongs to you, please provide access to it. The site appears to be loading insecure (HTTP) resources, which may indicate SSL configuration issues. When we embed this site inside your secure (HTTPS) website via iframe, it generates mixed content errors in the browser console when users click on products.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nTo resolve this issue, the external site must be fully secured and serve all content over HTTPS. Otherwise, modern browsers will continue blocking those insecure resources.\r\nbefore submit i add a capcha code to prevent spam activities on the contact form', 49),
(1154, 2, 'Adding blog page', '2026-02-25 10:25:43', '2026-02-25 15:04:45', '2026-02-25', '2026-02-25 04:55:43', 'sandy sir assigned a given below task \r\nHi @Karanbir Singh  please work on these points shared by Beth:\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Can you add a blog page (yes, I\'ve come around to wanting a blog)?\r\n\r\n2. Is there a way to connect the patterns page to underneath where people post their finished projects. Here\'s what I am thinking. If a person includes the pattern of the item they finished, it can then also be displayed on the Patterns section. Is this possible? I still want a separate patterns section so that people can post their patterns without including project.\r\n\r\n\r\ndeveloper notes   task completed developed oe blog structure  where user can add blogs and also structurize the share project task when user create share project   immidiately patterns also created', 1);
